{"tid":1630252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係時候補貨了","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:21:49.000Z","uid":59806,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2395d76c6492384c755f80cd7d219a57e04826a0","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cj8uJyq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCj8uJyq.jpg&h=74f81728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6200+60928都係388<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5a693256085865e35aa8c442f05fe76420439b","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe471cb823c077fbd8a3ed143f06eac7706480c","tid":1630252,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:53:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"487a3ddd175a2a36445273ce17c8d79d582480ab","tid":1630252,"uid":326759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"咩app？"},{"pid":"cf139cccbc3f8a01d712b29b1ce99ec8add831fe","tid":1630252,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"522ecd70a66499a893501f8899315c9f1c87e239","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"487a3ddd175a2a36445273ce17c8d79d582480ab","tid":1630252,"uid":326759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:54:08.000Z","msg":"咩app？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"hktvmall<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f941e37883a62ed66bf96b0884fd7572f304009","tid":1630252,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:24.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1d25abf347fbce9da108c84c8ddea5efe96a838e","tid":1630252,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339d452ccd341c8744f8f0026fa62fc850982b67","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fd73ff3c84ee8496d36f470db26f8067f8df60","tid":1630252,"uid":19945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"有用post永遠推唔到<br />\n大家幫下小弟手可以嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［緊急幫推］可唔可以搵文宣組即時整18區開花poster<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630136</a>"},{"pid":"a563b3593370c1a2128b1ad0b6dd6443b08e84bc","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae62707492156c51cfd72292b4256173f82675c","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff487814af598989ffe9e7c1b0ab1daeef216d1d","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c119d0e6c2169463753c12f242f10dd4de5a1d3b","tid":1630252,"uid":256238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:03:41.000Z","msg":"BBC記者想要的士撞人原片同埋聯絡拍片嗰個人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630113</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de9632e73d76ddfd170bd61b34ef54d493fe60b8","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56c529be35a512ad61a838ad26b6feac758940a","tid":1630252,"uid":53702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"wiki好波"},{"pid":"58c996c12c13a52bb8ae3474c35f59bccd7880a0","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385703ed73bf53c7720cb9b3aeacccaf7fda2618","tid":1630252,"uid":59806,"like":0,"dislike":